[
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "40",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"05162\" class=\"\">Comfort</st>, <st data-num=\"05162\" class=\"\">comfort</st> my <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">people</st>,\u201d <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st> your<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "1"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "40",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"01696\" class=\"\">Speak</st> <st data-num=\"05921 03820\">kindly</st> to<n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st><n id=\"2\" /> and <st data-num=\"07121 0413\">tell</st> her<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">that</st> her <st data-num=\"06635\" class=\"\">time of warfare</st> <st data-num=\"04390\" class=\"\">is over</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">that</st> her <st data-num=\"05771\" class=\"\">punishment</st> <st data-num=\"07521\" class=\"\">is completed</st>.<n id=\"4\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03027 03068\">Lord</st></span> has <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">made</st> her <st data-num=\"03947\" class=\"\">pay</st> <st data-num=\"03718\" class=\"\">double</st><n id=\"5\" /> for <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> her <st data-num=\"02403\" class=\"\">sins</st>.\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "2"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "40",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">A <st data-num=\"06963\" class=\"\">voice</st> <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">cries out</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">\u201cIn the <st data-num=\"04057\" class=\"\">wilderness</st> <st data-num=\"06437\" class=\"\">clear</st> a <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">way</st> for the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>;<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03474\" class=\"\">build</st> a <st data-num=\"03474\" class=\"\">level</st> <st data-num=\"04546\" class=\"\">road</st><n id=\"1\" /> through the <st data-num=\"06160\" class=\"\">rift valley</st><n id=\"2\" /> for our <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "3"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "40",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">Every</st> <st data-num=\"01516\" class=\"\">valley</st> must be <st data-num=\"05375\" class=\"\">elevated</st><p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">every</st> <st data-num=\"02022\" class=\"\">mountain</st> and <st data-num=\"01389\" class=\"\">hill</st> <st data-num=\"08213\" class=\"\">leveled</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"06121\" class=\"\">rough terrain</st> will <st data-num=\"01961\" class=\"\">become</st> a <st data-num=\"04334\" class=\"\">level plain</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">the <st data-num=\"07406\" class=\"\">rugged landscape</st> a <st data-num=\"01237\" class=\"\">wide valley</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "4"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "40",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"03519\" class=\"\">splendor</st><n id=\"1\" /> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> will be <st data-num=\"01540\" class=\"\">revealed</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> <st data-num=\"01320\" class=\"\">people</st><n id=\"2\" /> will <st data-num=\"07200\" class=\"\">see</st> it <st data-num=\"03162\" class=\"\">at the same time</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">For</st><n id=\"3\" /> the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"06310 03068\">Lord</st></span> has <st data-num=\"01696\" class=\"\">decreed</st> it.\u201d<n id=\"4\" /></p>",
    "verse": "5"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "40",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">A <st data-num=\"06963\" class=\"\">voice</st> <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st>, \u201c<st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">Cry out</st>!\u201d<p class=\"poetry\">Another <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">asks</st>,<n id=\"1\" /> \u201c<st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">What</st> should I <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">cry out</st>?\u201d<p class=\"poetry\">The first voice responds:<n id=\"2\" /> \u201c<st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">All</st> <st data-num=\"01320\" class=\"\">people</st> are like <st data-num=\"02682\" class=\"\">grass</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> their <st data-num=\"02617\" class=\"\">promises</st><n id=\"4\" /> are like the <st data-num=\"06731\" class=\"\">flowers</st> in the <st data-num=\"07704\" class=\"\">field</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "6"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "40",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"02682\" class=\"\">grass</st> <st data-num=\"03001\" class=\"\">dries up</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">the <st data-num=\"06731\" class=\"\">flowers</st> <st data-num=\"05034\" class=\"\">wither</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03588\" class=\"\">when</st> the <st data-num=\"07307\" class=\"\">wind</st> sent by the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span><n id=\"1\" /> <st data-num=\"05380\" class=\"\">blows</st> on them.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0403\" class=\"\">Surely</st> <st data-num=\"05971\" class=\"\">humanity</st><n id=\"2\" /> is like <st data-num=\"02682\" class=\"\">grass</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "7"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "40",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">The <st data-num=\"02682\" class=\"\">grass</st> <st data-num=\"03001\" class=\"\">dries up</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">the <st data-num=\"06731\" class=\"\">flowers</st> <st data-num=\"05034\" class=\"\">wither</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">but the <st data-num=\"01697\" class=\"\">decree</st> of our <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">is</st> <st data-num=\"05769\" class=\"\">forever</st> <st data-num=\"06965\" class=\"\">reliable</st>.\u201d<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "8"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "40",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05927\" class=\"\">Go up</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> a <st data-num=\"01364\" class=\"\">high</st> <st data-num=\"02022\" class=\"\">mountain</st>, O <st data-num=\"01319\" class=\"\">herald</st> <st data-num=\"06726\" class=\"\">Zion</st>.<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07311\" class=\"\">Shout</st> <st data-num=\"06963\" class=\"\">out</st> <st data-num=\"03581\" class=\"\">loudly</st>, O <st data-num=\"01319\" class=\"\">herald</st> <st data-num=\"03389\" class=\"\">Jerusalem</st>!<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"07311\" class=\"\">Shout</st>, <st data-num=\"0408\" class=\"\">don\u2019t</st> <st data-num=\"03372\" class=\"\">be afraid</st>!<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">Say</st> to the <st data-num=\"05892\" class=\"\">towns</st> of <st data-num=\"03063\" class=\"\">Judah</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">Here</st> is your <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>!\u201d </p>",
    "verse": "9"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "40",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">Look</st>, the <st data-num=\"0136\">Sovereign</st> <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"0935\" class=\"\">comes</st> as a <st data-num=\"02389\" class=\"\">victorious warrior</st>;<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">his <st data-num=\"02220\" class=\"\">military power</st> <st data-num=\"04910\" class=\"\">establishes</st> his <st data-num=\"04910\" class=\"\">rule</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02009\" class=\"\">Look</st>, his <st data-num=\"07939\" class=\"\">reward</st> is <st data-num=\"0854\" class=\"\">with</st> him;<p class=\"poetry\">his <st data-num=\"06468\" class=\"\">prize</st> goes <st data-num=\"06440\" class=\"\">before</st> him.<n id=\"3\" /></p>",
    "verse": "10"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "40",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Like a <st data-num=\"07462\" class=\"\">shepherd</st> he <st data-num=\"07462\" class=\"\">tends</st> his <st data-num=\"05739\" class=\"\">flock</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">he <st data-num=\"06908\" class=\"\">gathers up</st> the <st data-num=\"02922\" class=\"\">lambs</st> with his <st data-num=\"02220\" class=\"\">arm</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">he <st data-num=\"05375\" class=\"\">carries</st> them <st data-num=\"02436\" class=\"\">close to</st> his <st data-num=\"02436\" class=\"\">heart</st>;<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">he <st data-num=\"05095\" class=\"\">leads</st> the <st data-num=\"05763\" class=\"\">ewes</st> <st data-num=\"05095\" class=\"\">along</st>.</p>",
    "verse": "11"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "40",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">Who</st> has <st data-num=\"04058\" class=\"\">measured out</st> the <st data-num=\"04325\" class=\"\">waters</st><n id=\"1\" /> in the <st data-num=\"08168\" class=\"\">hollow of</st> his <st data-num=\"08168\" class=\"\">hand</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">or <st data-num=\"02239\" class=\"\">carefully</st><n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"08505\" class=\"\">measured</st> the <st data-num=\"08064\" class=\"\">sky</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">or <st data-num=\"07991\" class=\"\">carefully</st> <st data-num=\"03557\" class=\"\">weighed</st><n id=\"4\" /> the <st data-num=\"06083\" class=\"\">soil</st> of the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">earth</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">or <st data-num=\"08254\" class=\"\">weighed</st> the <st data-num=\"02022\" class=\"\">mountains</st> in a <st data-num=\"06425\" class=\"\">balance</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">or the <st data-num=\"01389\" class=\"\">hills</st> on <st data-num=\"03976\" class=\"\">scales</st>?<n id=\"5\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "12"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "40",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">Who</st> <st data-num=\"08505\" class=\"\">comprehends</st><n id=\"1\" /> the <st data-num=\"07307\" class=\"\">mind</st><n id=\"2\" /> of the <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span>,<p class=\"poetry\">or <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">gives</st> him <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">instruction</st> as his <st data-num=\"0376 06098\">counselor</st>?<n id=\"3\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "13"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "40",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">From <st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">whom</st> does he <st data-num=\"03289 0995\">receive directions</st>?<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">Who<n id=\"2\" /> <st data-num=\"03925\" class=\"\">teaches</st> him the <st data-num=\"04941\" class=\"\">correct</st> <st data-num=\"0734\" class=\"\">way</st> to do things,<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">or <st data-num=\"03925\" class=\"\">imparts</st> <st data-num=\"01847\" class=\"\">knowledge</st> to him,<p class=\"poetry\">or <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">instructs</st> him in <st data-num=\"08394\" class=\"\">skillful</st> <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">design</st>?<n id=\"4\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "14"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "40",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"02005\" class=\"\">Look</st>, the <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">nations</st> are like a <st data-num=\"04752\" class=\"\">drop</st> in a <st data-num=\"01805\" class=\"\">bucket</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">they are <st data-num=\"02803\" class=\"\">regarded</st> as <st data-num=\"07834\" class=\"\">dust</st> on the <st data-num=\"03976\" class=\"\">scales</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">He <st data-num=\"05190\" class=\"\">lifts</st><n id=\"1\" /> the <st data-num=\"0339\" class=\"\">coastlands</st><n id=\"2\" /> as <st data-num=\"02005\" class=\"\">if</st> they were <st data-num=\"01851\" class=\"\">dust</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "15"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "40",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">Not</st> even <st data-num=\"03844\" class=\"\">Lebanon</st> <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">could supply</st> <st data-num=\"01767\" class=\"\">enough</st> <st data-num=\"01197\" class=\"\">firewood</st> for a sacrifice;<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">its <st data-num=\"02416\" class=\"\">wild animals</st> <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">would not provide</st> <st data-num=\"01767\" class=\"\">enough</st> <st data-num=\"05930\" class=\"\">burnt offerings</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "16"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "40",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">All</st> the <st data-num=\"01471\" class=\"\">nations</st> are <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">insignificant</st> <st data-num=\"05048\" class=\"\">before</st> him;<p class=\"poetry\">they are <st data-num=\"02803\" class=\"\">regarded</st> as <st data-num=\"0657\" class=\"\">absolutely</st> <st data-num=\"08414\" class=\"\">nothing</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "17"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "40",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">To</st> <st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">whom</st> can you <st data-num=\"01819\" class=\"\">compare</st> <st data-num=\"0410\" class=\"\">God</st>?<p class=\"poetry\">To <st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">what</st> <st data-num=\"01823\" class=\"\">image</st> can you <st data-num=\"06186\" class=\"\">liken</st> him?</p>",
    "verse": "18"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "40",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">A <st data-num=\"02796\" class=\"\">craftsman</st> <st data-num=\"05258\" class=\"\">casts</st><n id=\"1\" /> an <st data-num=\"06459\" class=\"\">idol</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">a <st data-num=\"06884\" class=\"\">metalsmith</st> <st data-num=\"07554\" class=\"\">overlays</st> it with <st data-num=\"02091\" class=\"\">gold</st><p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"06884\" class=\"\">forges</st> <st data-num=\"03701\" class=\"\">silver</st> <st data-num=\"07577\" class=\"\">chains</st> for it.</p>",
    "verse": "19"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "40",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">To make a <st data-num=\"08641\" class=\"\">contribution</st> one <st data-num=\"0977\" class=\"\">selects</st> <st data-num=\"06086\" class=\"\">wood</st> that will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"07537\" class=\"\">rot</st>;<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">he then <st data-num=\"01245\" class=\"\">seeks</st> a <st data-num=\"02450\" class=\"\">skilled</st> <st data-num=\"02796\" class=\"\">craftsman</st><p class=\"poetry\">to <st data-num=\"03559\" class=\"\">make</st><n id=\"2\" /> an <st data-num=\"06459\" class=\"\">idol</st> that will <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"04131\" class=\"\">fall over</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "20"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "40",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Do you <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">know</st>?<p class=\"poetry\">Do you <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">hear</st>?<p class=\"poetry\">Has it <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> been <st data-num=\"05046\" class=\"\">told</st> to you since the very <st data-num=\"07218\" class=\"\">beginning</st>?<p class=\"poetry\">Have you <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"0995\" class=\"\">understood</st> from the time the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">earth\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"04146\" class=\"\">foundations</st> were made?</p>",
    "verse": "21"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "40",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">He is the one who <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">sits</st> <st data-num=\"05921\" class=\"\">on</st> the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">earth\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"02329\" class=\"\">horizon</st>;<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">its <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">inhabitants</st> are like <st data-num=\"02284\" class=\"\">grasshoppers</st> before him.<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">He is the one who <st data-num=\"05186\" class=\"\">stretches out</st> the <st data-num=\"08064\" class=\"\">sky</st> like a <st data-num=\"01852\" class=\"\">thin curtain</st>,<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"04969\" class=\"\">spreads</st> it <st data-num=\"04969\" class=\"\">out</st><n id=\"4\" /> like a <st data-num=\"03427\" class=\"\">pitched</st> <st data-num=\"0168\" class=\"\">tent</st>.<n id=\"5\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "22"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "40",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">He is the one who <st data-num=\"05414\" class=\"\">reduces</st> <st data-num=\"07336\" class=\"\">rulers</st> to <st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">nothing</st>;<p class=\"poetry\">he <st data-num=\"06213\" class=\"\">makes</st> the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">earth\u2019s</st> <st data-num=\"08199\" class=\"\">leaders</st> <st data-num=\"08414\" class=\"\">insignificant</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "23"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "40",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0637\" class=\"\">Indeed</st>, they are <st data-num=\"01077\" class=\"\">barely</st> <st data-num=\"05193\" class=\"\">planted</st>;<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0637\" class=\"\">yes</st>, they are <st data-num=\"01077\" class=\"\">barely</st> <st data-num=\"02232\" class=\"\">sown</st>;<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0637\" class=\"\">yes</st>, <st data-num=\"01503\" class=\"\">they</st> <st data-num=\"01077\" class=\"\">barely</st> <st data-num=\"08327\" class=\"\">take root</st> in the <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">earth</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and <st data-num=\"01571\" class=\"\">then</st> he <st data-num=\"05398\" class=\"\">blows</st> on them, causing them to <st data-num=\"03001\" class=\"\">dry up</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">and the <st data-num=\"05591\" class=\"\">wind</st> <st data-num=\"05375\" class=\"\">carries</st> them <st data-num=\"05375\" class=\"\">away</st> like <st data-num=\"07179\" class=\"\">straw</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "24"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "40",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">\u201c<st data-num=\"0413\" class=\"\">To</st> <st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">whom</st> can you <st data-num=\"01819\" class=\"\">compare</st> me? Whom do I <st data-num=\"07737\" class=\"\">resemble</st>?\u201d<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">says</st> the <st data-num=\"06918\" class=\"\">Holy One</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "25"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "40",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"05375 05869 07200\">Look up</st> at the <st data-num=\"04791\" class=\"\">sky</st>!<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04310\" class=\"\">Who</st> <st data-num=\"01254\" class=\"\">created</st> all <st data-num=\"0428\" class=\"\">these</st> heavenly lights?<n id=\"2\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">He is the one who <st data-num=\"03318\" class=\"\">leads out</st> their <st data-num=\"04557 06635\">ranks</st>;<n id=\"3\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">he <st data-num=\"07121\" class=\"\">calls</st> them <st data-num=\"03605\" class=\"\">all</st> by <st data-num=\"08034\" class=\"\">name</st>.<p class=\"poetry\">Because of his <st data-num=\"07230\" class=\"\">absolute</st> <st data-num=\"0202\" class=\"\">power</st> and <st data-num=\"0533\" class=\"\">awesome</st> <st data-num=\"03581\" class=\"\">strength</st>,<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"0376\" class=\"\">one</st> of them <st data-num=\"05737\" class=\"\">is missing</st>. </p>",
    "verse": "26"
  },
  {
    "bookname": "Isaiah",
    "chapter": "40",
    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"04100\" class=\"\">Why</st> do you <st data-num=\"0559\" class=\"\">say</st>, <st data-num=\"03290\" class=\"\">Jacob</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">Why do you <st data-num=\"01696\" class=\"\">say</st>, <st data-num=\"03478\" class=\"\">Israel</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">\u201cThe <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> <st data-num=\"05641\" class=\"\">is not aware of</st> <st data-num=\"01870\" class=\"\">what is happening to</st> me;<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">my <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st> <st data-num=\"05674\" class=\"\">is not concerned with</st> my <st data-num=\"04941\" class=\"\">vindication</st>\u201d?<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
    "verse": "27"
  },
  {
