    "text": "<p class=\"poetry\">Do you <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"03045\" class=\"\">know</st>?<p class=\"poetry\">Have you <st data-num=\"0518 03808\">not</st> <st data-num=\"08085\" class=\"\">heard</st>?<p class=\"poetry\">The <span class=\"smcaps\"><st data-num=\"03068\" class=\"\">Lord</st></span> is an <st data-num=\"05769\" class=\"\">eternal</st> <st data-num=\"0430\" class=\"\">God</st>,<p class=\"poetry\">the <st data-num=\"01254\" class=\"\">Creator</st> of the <st data-num=\"07098\" class=\"\">whole</st> <st data-num=\"0776\" class=\"\">earth</st>.<n id=\"1\" /> <p class=\"poetry\">He does <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">not</st> <st data-num=\"03286 03021\">get</st> <st data-num=\"03286\" class=\"\">tired</st> <st data-num=\"03808\" class=\"\">or</st> <st data-num=\"03021\" class=\"\">weary</st>;<p class=\"poetry\"><st data-num=\"0369\" class=\"\">there is no</st> <st data-num=\"02714\" class=\"\">limit</st> to his <st data-num=\"08394\" class=\"\">wisdom</st>.<n id=\"2\" /> </p>",
